        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for the letter commending <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">8692</hi>]. CD "was not at all sure the work was worth publishing".</p> 
            <p>Acknowledges receipt of some pamphlets from PM, which his wife will translate.</p> 
<p>Regretfully must refuse PM’s offer to translate <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> since it has been promised to another.</p>  
<p>Has now received PM’s <hi rend="italic">Physiology of pleasure</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Fisiologia del piacere</hi> (1870)].</p> 
        </abstract>
